                                <p class="processing-subtitle" style="color: var(--color-text-gray); font-size: 0.85rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; text-align: center; font-family: var(--font-accent);">Atenuando ruido fractal mediante filtro espectral SFA (f<sub>base</sub> = 7.25 Hz)</p>
                                <div class="processing-progress-bar" style="width: 100%; max-width: 400px; height: 6px; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05); border-radius: 3px; overflow: hidden; margin: 0 auto 0.5rem; border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.02);">
                                    <div class="progress-fill" id="processing-progress-fill" style="width: 0%; height: 100%; background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--color-primary-gold), #10b981); transition: width 0.1s linear; box-shadow: 0 0 10px var(--color-primary-gold);"></div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="processing-progress-percentage" id="processing-progress-percentage" style="text-align: center; font-family: var(--font-accent); color: var(--color-primary-gold); font-weight: bold; font-size: 0.9rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">0%</div>
